== Abrabo ahyɛaseɛ ne adesua ==
Yɛ wo Johnson  Oforisuo bosome no da ɛtɔ so edunan wɔ afe edunkron ne eduonum nsɔn mu. Ɔkɔɔ Atebubu nteteyɛ suapɔn a ɛndɛ yɛ frɛ no Atebubu Suapɔn ma Adesua  wɔ Bono Apueɛ mantemu wɔ Gana, ɛhɔ na onya ne akyerɛkyerɛ nteteyɛ krataa.  Ɔwie sukuu no, ɔhyɛ na adekyerɛ adwuma no ase ansa ɔrekɔ mmarahyɛbadwam.

== Politics ==
Johnson hyɛ ne amanyɔ adwuma no ase wɔ afe edunkron ne eduokron mienu mu (1992) wɔ abre a ɔbɛ yɛ frankaa tu ni ma amanyɔkuo [[NDC|National Democratic Congress]] (NDC) ma Bosome-Freho mpasua so abre a wɔ yɛ ahoboa ama  [[1992 Ghana Mmarahyɛ badwa abatoɔ|1992 Gana mmarahyɛbadwam abatoɔ no.]] Wɔ di kan yi no ma no kɔɔ mmarahyɛbadwam a edikan wɔ kwasafoman a ɛtɔ so anan wɔ 1992 abatoɔ no mu, eno akyi no na ɔhyɛ ne offese adwuma no ase wɔ ɔpɛpɔn da a ɛtɔ so nsɔn wɔ afe 1993 mu. Ɛno akyi no na ɔhwere ne akonnwa no ma  Gabriel Yaw Amoah  a ogyina ma [[NPP|New Patriotic Party]] amanyɔkuo wɔ afe [[1996 Ghanaian Abatoɔ|1996 Gana abatoɔ kese no mu.]]

